                </structure>
                <structure>
                    <property name="name">[LC CCY][SG/DO Amount (FCY)]</property>
                    <expression name="expression">dataSetRow["SG_CCY"] + dataSetRow["SG_FCY_AMT"]</expression>
                    <property name="dataType">any</property>
                </structure>
                <structure>
                    <property name="name">DETAIL</property>
                    <expression name="expression">'Dear Sirs,'+

'We regret to inform you that the Bills of Lading relating to the number of packages or pieces mentioned below, of which we claim to be the rightful Owners or Owner’s agent have been lost or have not yet been received by M/S.'+ dataSetRow["APPL_NM"] +'.'+

'Without requiring the surrender of the Bills of Lading and in consideration of your so doing we hereby unreservedly undertake to indemnify you, the ship, her owners and agents holding all the aforementioned, free from any harm whatsoever and howsoever arising directly or indirectly as a result of releasing without the production and surrender of the Bills of Lading, and we further undertake and agree that the misdescription or incorrectness (whether fraudulent or otherwise) of any statement relating to the contents, quality, quantity, weight, numbers, marks and/or value of the packages or pieces inserted hereunder shall not limit or affect in any way whatsoever liability or that of our Bankers hereunder.'+

'It is our intention that the foregoing indemnity includes all legal costs whether or not a writ be issued, so as to cover all the expenses of any consultants with and instructions to your legal advisers that may in your opinion be necessary.'+

'Our object in granting you this indemnity, is to secure that the concession you are making to us in releasing the number of packages or pieces as mentioned below without production and surrender of the Bills of Lading, shall not place you in any worse position than would be the case if you released in the recognized and required manner against Bills of Lading.'</expression>
                    <property name="dataType">any</property>
                </structure>
                <structure>
                    <property name="name">[Issue Date]</property>
                    <expression name="expression">'Issue Date:'+row["ISSUE_DT"]</expression>
                    <property name="dataType">any</property>
                </structure>
            </list-property>
